  ('dietitian-moex-01883', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關洗潔劑使用安全性之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["一般而言，蔬菜中洗潔劑的殘留量會比水果類高", "目前尚無有關硬性洗潔劑影響人體安全的報告，故此類清潔劑尚可使用於食品之清潔", "軟性洗潔劑的烷基長度愈長，其毒性愈低", "一般而言，陽離子型界面活性劑之毒性較陰離子型界面活性劑為低"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01884', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關過氧化氫在食品上之使用，下列何者正確？', '["為我國禁用之防腐劑", "可使用於麵粉及其製品等食品中", "可使用於魚肉煉製品中", "食品中允許殘留量為0.05%"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01885', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關生魚片之檢驗標準，何者正確？', '["生菌數：100,000 CFU/g以下", "大腸桿菌群：陰性", "大腸桿菌：1,000 MPN/g以下", "揮發性鹽基態氮：15 mg/100 g以上"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
